---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
const { cta_url } = Astro.props;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Arcane Stance by Takeshi Mizuki reveals the hidden power of body language. Learn techniques to master non-verbal communication, enhance influence, and improve personal and professional relationships.">
    <meta name="keywords" content="Arcane Stance, Takeshi Mizuki, body language, non-verbal communication, personal influence, professional impact, hidden power of gestures, communication skills">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Arcane Stance by Takeshi Mizuki">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Unlock the hidden power of body language with Arcane Stance by Takeshi Mizuki. This guide provides techniques to enhance influence, boost professional impact, and deepen personal connections.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="/ArcaneStance.png">
    <meta property="og:url" content={cta_url}>
    <meta property="og:type" content="book">
    <title>Arcane Stance by Takeshi Mizuki</title>
    <link rel="canonical" href={cta_url}>
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
  </head>
  <body>
    <main class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 mb-8 mt-12 sm:mt-12 sm:mb-12 sm:px-6 md:mt-32 md:mb-20 xl:mt-23 xl:mb-24">
      <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-8">
        <div class="mb-12 md:max-w-1xl md:mx-auto lg:col-span-8">
          <h1
            class="mt-1 text-5xl tracking-tight leading-16 font-extrabold sm:leading-none sm:text-6xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl uppercase"
          >
            Arcane Stance<br class="hidden md:inline" /><span class="underline">by Takeshi Mizuki</span>
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            Arcane Stance by Takeshi Mizuki reveals the secret power of body language and how it can transform your life. This compelling guide introduces you to hidden techniques and methods to master non-verbal communication, enhancing your ability to influence, connect, and succeed.</p>
          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            With actionable strategies and practical advice, Black provides a roadmap to unlocking the hidden potential within your gestures and expressions. Whether youâ€™re looking to improve your personal presence, boost your professional impact, or deepen your relationships, this book offers the tools you need to become a master of body language.</p>

          <p class="mt-3 text-muted dark:text-slate-400 ml-2 rtl:ml-0 rtl:mr-2">
            <b>WARNING: This Book Will Be Removed Soon. Hurry and Get It Now.</b>
          </p>

          <div class="mt-5 sm:mt-8 sm:flex sm:justify-center lg:justify-start">
            <div>
              <a
                href={cta_url}
                target="_blank"
                class="w-full flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-3 border border-transparent text-base leading-6 rounded-md font-semibold text-white bg-book-theme hover:bg-book-hover focus:outline-none transition duration-300 ease-in-out md:py-4 md:text-lg md:px-10"
              >
                Get It Now
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="mt-12 relative sm:max-w-lg sm:mx-auto lg:mt-0 lg:max-w-none lg:mx-0 lg:col-span-4 lg:flex lg:items-center"
        >
          <a class="book-container" href={cta_url}>
            <div class="book">
              <Image
                src="/ArcaneStance.png"
                width={300}
                height={600}
                alt="Arcane Stance by Takeshi Mizuki Book Cover"
                format="avif"
                loading="eager"
              />
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>